<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 18:08:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以上帝之名进行种族清洗：唯一对加沙“后天”有计划的以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/ethnic-cleansing-in-gods-name-the-only-israelis-with-a-plan-for-the-day-after-in-gaza/0000018d-55e0-d997-adff-ddfa9b490000</link><description>周日，约 5,000 名定居者聚集在耶路撒冷，庆祝他们为重新定居加沙地带所做的努力，并使弥赛亚的到来更近了一步。他们在以色列仍然是少数派，这一事实并没有引起他们的关注</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 17:13:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/ethnic-cleansing-in-gods-name-the-only-israelis-with-a-plan-for-the-day-after-in-gaza/0000018d-55e0-d997-adff-ddfa9b490000</guid></item><item><title>周一，在约旦河西岸发生的四起事件中，五名巴勒斯坦人被以色列军队开火打死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/five-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-army-fire-in-four-separate-west-bank-incidents/0000018d-5599-d0fc-a9bd-5fddaadd0000</link><description>以色列军队称，一名年轻人在亚蒙村向以色列国防军士兵开枪后被杀；另外两名巴勒斯坦人在杜拉被杀，另一名青年在以色列特科亚定居点附近被杀，另一名青年在拉马拉附近被杀</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 16:27:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/five-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-army-fire-in-four-separate-west-bank-incidents/0000018d-5599-d0fc-a9bd-5fddaadd0000</guid></item><item><title>在内塔尼亚胡的鼓励下，犹太人至上和反民主的狂热狂欢</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/an-orgy-of-jewish-supremacy-and-antidemocratic-euphoria-encouraged-by-netanyahu/0000018d-556b-d0fc-a9bd-5f7f8b540000</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登下次与本杰明·内塔尼亚胡谈论中东重组问题时应该记住周日极右翼会议上呼吁重新安置加沙的场景</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 16:26:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/an-orgy-of-jewish-supremacy-and-antidemocratic-euphoria-encouraged-by-netanyahu/0000018d-556b-d0fc-a9bd-5f7f8b540000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡受贿案辩护律师要求辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-defense-attorney-in-bribery-case-asks-to-step-down/0000018d-54e1-d1b6-aded-5fe929d20000</link><description>总理表示，提出这一要求的原因是他的律师的家人生病了。在另外两起刑事案件中代表内塔尼亚胡的律师阿米特·哈达德表示，他也愿意在贿赂案中代表他</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 15:52:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-defense-attorney-in-bribery-case-asks-to-step-down/0000018d-54e1-d1b6-aded-5fe929d20000</guid></item><item><title>据《华尔街日报》报道，近东救济工程处在加沙的大约 10% 员工与哈马斯、伊斯兰圣战组织有联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/wsj-about-10-percent-of-unrwa-employees-in-gaza-have-ties-to-hamas-islamic-jihad/0000018d-5565-d8cc-a1fd-576f89eb0000</link><description>以色列官员向《华尔街日报》报道称，参与加沙哈马斯活动的联合国巴勒斯坦难民机构（近东救济工程处）雇员数量“不仅仅是几个害群之马”。随着指控的继续调查，九个国家已暂时停止向该组织提供资金</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 15:36:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/wsj-about-10-percent-of-unrwa-employees-in-gaza-have-ties-to-hamas-islamic-jihad/0000018d-5565-d8cc-a1fd-576f89eb0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列人民将解决加沙问题”：内塔尼亚胡的部长们在极右翼会议上支持驱逐巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-people-of-israel-will-settle-gaza-netanyahu-ministers-urge-palestinians-expulsion/0000018d-5495-d1b6-aded-5fdd570c0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的通讯部长在台上宣称，“自愿”[移民]有时是你强加的情况，直到他们同意为止。”他揭露了“以色列胜利会议”的真实信息：转移或驱逐，来自加沙的巴勒斯坦人</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 15:32:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-people-of-israel-will-settle-gaza-netanyahu-ministers-urge-palestinians-expulsion/0000018d-5495-d1b6-aded-5fdd570c0000</guid></item><item><title>不仅是加沙：自战争以来，西岸巴勒斯坦人买不起食物和药品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/not-only-gaza-west-bank-palestinians-cannot-afford-food-and-meds-since-the-war/0000018d-556e-d0fc-a9bd-5f7f03930000</link><description>加沙战争对约旦河西岸的经济造成严重破坏：商店关门，企业停止接受非现金付款，巴勒斯坦工人不吃饭，孩子们几乎没有足够的食物</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 14:28:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/not-only-gaza-west-bank-palestinians-cannot-afford-food-and-meds-since-the-war/0000018d-556e-d0fc-a9bd-5f7f03930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在海法发生撞击后受重伤；袭击者用斧头射击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-seriously-wounded-after-ramming-in-haifa-assailant-with-axe-shot/0000018d-5489-dfdc-a5ad-deff8ba60000</link><description>这名士兵在海军基地附近被一名袭击者碾压受伤，袭击者随后携带斧头下车，被一名以色列国防军军官开枪射击。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 12:27:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-seriously-wounded-after-ramming-in-haifa-assailant-with-axe-shot/0000018d-5489-dfdc-a5ad-deff8ba60000</guid></item><item><title>想离开加沙吗？支付我们 10,000 美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/want-out-of-gaza-pay-us-10-000/0000018d-54ee-df5c-a1ad-54ff690e0000</link><description>在加沙，在流离失所的加沙人试图躲避以色列的炸弹的影响下，进入埃及的拉法口岸的贿赂业正在蓬勃发展。埃及否认这一点，但一名埃及研究人员表示，“开罗最高官员”参与其中</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 11:46:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/want-out-of-gaza-pay-us-10-000/0000018d-54ee-df5c-a1ad-54ff690e0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦诉拜登：“我的家人被我的钱杀害了。”新闻。拜登可以结束这一切”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/my-family-is-being-killed-on-my-dime-pres-biden-could-put-an-end-to-this/0000018d-54b3-df5c-a1ad-54f7a03e0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 10:28:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/my-family-is-being-killed-on-my-dime-pres-biden-could-put-an-end-to-this/0000018d-54b3-df5c-a1ad-54f7a03e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会听取因支持国际法院案件而驱逐左翼 MK 的论点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-knesset-hears-arguments-for-expulsion-of-left-wing-mk-over-support-for-icj-case/0000018d-54a5-d0fc-a9bd-5efd2da80000</link><description>奥弗·卡西夫在听证会上表示，“虽然那些呼吁用火或原子弹摧毁加沙的人坐在内阁会议桌旁，但我面临着‘支持武装斗争’毫无根据的指控的弹劾。”弹劾动议预计将遇到法律困难</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 10:09:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-knesset-hears-arguments-for-expulsion-of-left-wing-mk-over-support-for-icj-case/0000018d-54a5-d0fc-a9bd-5efd2da80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长：重新安置加沙的呼吁“超级合法”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/israels-education-minister-calls-to-resettle-gaza-are-super-legitimate/0000018d-543f-dfdc-a5ad-de7f0e290000</link><description>约阿夫·基什部长对支持耶路撒冷定居点会议的分裂性的唯一批评是其时机。部长甘茨所在政党的成员表示，这一事件“分裂了以色列社会并增加了对政府的不信任”</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 09:18:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/israels-education-minister-calls-to-resettle-gaza-are-super-legitimate/0000018d-543f-dfdc-a5ad-de7f0e290000</guid></item><item><title>加沙火箭弹袭击特拉维夫；报告：调解员向哈马斯提出以色列商定的人质协议框架</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article-live/netanyahu-gaps-remain-as-talks-on-new-hostage-deal-with-hamas-progress-in-paris-summit/0000018d-52f1-d7e4-a7ad-5af7a2c00006</link><description>卡塔尔总理称人质交易取得进展 ■ 一名士兵在海法袭击中受重伤 ■ 两名士兵在以色列北部被真主党火箭弹轻伤 ■ 奥地利、罗马尼亚等国因涉嫌参与哈马斯屠杀而暂停向近东救济工程处提供资金</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 03:58:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article-live/netanyahu-gaps-remain-as-talks-on-new-hostage-deal-with-hamas-progress-in-paris-summit/0000018d-52f1-d7e4-a7ad-5af7a2c00006</guid></item><item><title>以色列表示巴黎峰会后对哈马斯人质协议进展的估计仍然存在巨大差距</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/amid-estimates-of-progress-on-hostage-deal-israel-says-wide-gaps-persist-after-summit/0000018d-51e3-d5c3-a9fd-75ff0c670000</link><description>一位消息人士告诉《国土报》，“如果以色列和哈马斯成功弥合关键差距，协议可能会在几天或几周内完成。”据报道，主要争议在于停火期限，但一名以色列官员称与卡塔尔和美国官员的会面是“积极的”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 21:34:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/amid-estimates-of-progress-on-hostage-deal-israel-says-wide-gaps-persist-after-summit/0000018d-51e3-d5c3-a9fd-75ff0c670000</guid></item><item><title>以哈马斯袭击造成的创伤为由，以色列大学考试中的大屠杀章节将被放弃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/citing-trauma-of-hamas-attack-holocaust-chapter-in-israeli-matric-exam-to-be-waived/0000018d-51ba-d12b-afcd-d1fe2ac90000</link><description>10 月 7 日之后，教育工作者在讲述犹太人在大屠杀期间的经历时面临着情感和心理上的困难，以色列教育部长表示尚未做出最终决定</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 21:19:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/citing-trauma-of-hamas-attack-holocaust-chapter-in-israeli-matric-exam-to-be-waived/0000018d-51ba-d12b-afcd-d1fe2ac90000</guid></item><item><title>斯莫特里奇推迟以色列 2024 年预算，以期纳入联盟资金并避免审查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/smotrich-delays-2024-budget-in-a-bid-to-include-coalition-funding-and-avoid-review/0000018d-5189-dfdc-a5ad-dbffc8fb0000</link><description>据信，斯莫特里奇试图避免审查，并将联盟资金“隐藏”在更大的预算中。如果预算在2月19日之前未获得批准，则需要全面削减700亿谢克尔</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 21:17:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/smotrich-delays-2024-budget-in-a-bid-to-include-coalition-funding-and-avoid-review/0000018d-5189-dfdc-a5ad-dbffc8fb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总统谴责国际法院对其言论的描述，称加沙有无辜的巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/herzog-blasts-icjs-portrayal-of-his-remarks-says-there-are-innocent-palestinians-in-gaza/0000018d-51cb-dfdc-a5ad-dbffce970000</link><description>国际法院的报告指出，赫尔佐格在 10 月 12 日的新闻发布会上谈到加沙的巴勒斯坦人时表示，“整个国家”应对这场大屠杀负责。周日，他说，“我对他们歪曲我的话的方式感到厌恶”，指责他们“支持捏造的法律争论”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 21:12:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/herzog-blasts-icjs-portrayal-of-his-remarks-says-there-are-innocent-palestinians-in-gaza/0000018d-51cb-dfdc-a5ad-dbffce970000</guid></item><item><title>谁真正决定拜登的以色列-加沙政策？从内圈向外，重要美国官员指南</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/mapping-the-biden-administration-on-israel-gaza-and-the-palestinians/0000018d-4f4b-d02c-a79f-4fdb83090000</link><description>10月7日之前，美国和以色列优先考虑以色列与沙特关系正常化。现在，拜登政府正试图释放哈马斯扣押的人质，阻止与真主党的战争，并在加沙的战争和人道主义灾难中打击以色列的外交地位。以下是负责处理一系列日益加剧的担忧的美国官员</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 20:13:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/mapping-the-biden-administration-on-israel-gaza-and-the-palestinians/0000018d-4f4b-d02c-a79f-4fdb83090000</guid></item><item><title>国家将向在加沙战斗中丧生的菲律宾裔以色列国防军士兵的父母授予公民身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/state-to-grant-citizenship-to-parents-of-filipino-israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-5189-d5c3-a9fd-75ddded40000</link><description>西德里克·加林 (Cydrick Garin) 和其他 20 名士兵在加沙的一座建筑倒塌中丧生。他的父母是来自菲律宾的民工，他的父亲在他出生后就被驱逐出境。他的母亲说：“他是菲律宾公民，但他将一生奉献给了他深爱的祖国以色列”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 20:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/state-to-grant-citizenship-to-parents-of-filipino-israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-5189-d5c3-a9fd-75ddded40000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟主席错误地暗示奥斯威辛集中营是波兰而非德国，引发波兰抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/eu-chief-erroneously-suggests-auschwitz-was-polish-not-german-sparking-protest-in-poland/0000018d-511e-d3ab-a5cf-539f2b7d0000</link><description>欧盟委员会主席乌苏拉·冯德莱恩随后发表帖子澄清奥斯维辛是纳粹德国的灭绝营。近年来，波兰严厉打击了公众对其在大屠杀中所扮演角色的批评</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 19:59:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/eu-chief-erroneously-suggests-auschwitz-was-polish-not-german-sparking-protest-in-poland/0000018d-511e-d3ab-a5cf-539f2b7d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>